#!/usr/bin/python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

# A simple script to update version number in spec, dsc or arch linux files
#
# (C) 2010 by Adrian Schr√∂ter <adrian@suse.de>
# (C) 2015 by Thomas Bechtold <tbechtold@suse.com>
